<br>
People will be throwing a fit and rightly so, but what makes you think they are going to have some kind of radar telling them at what level it isn't appropriate to steal anymore? Do you think they are just going to say to themselves &quot;Oh, we've reached level 55, we're not going to be asses anymore, no sir, we've developed morals&quot;? No, they're not. These two guys are just an example, but it goes for anyone who displays the type of attitude they have displayed. A complete inability to be respectful of others.<br>
<br>
Why is the focus on what level the mob in question was? The focus should be on the attitude displayed when they are confronted. Did they continue to KS you after talking to them? Did they intentionally train you as repayment for confronting them? Did they then verbally harrass you?<br>
<br>
If the answers are &quot;yes&quot;, well, then it doesn't matter what level it happened at, because if they are doing it at level 9 without repercusions, then they will be doing it at level 55 too, and I don't think anyone wants that. Granted, I've never reported anyone, luckily have never been in the situation to need to, but I just don't feel like there should be some free pass to be an ass until you reach higher levels.<br>
 <p>Narie<br>
